1. Add PolicyType
POST
http://localhost:8080/api/policy-types

Request Body (valid):

{
  "typeName": "Life"
}

❌ Invalid (empty):

{
  "typeName": ""
}

2. Update PolicyType
PUT
http://localhost:8080/api/policy-types/1

Request Body (valid):

{
  "typeName": "Health"
}

❌ Invalid (empty):

{
  "typeName": ""
}

3. Get All PolicyTypes
GET
http://localhost:8080/api/policy-types

4. Get PolicyType by ID
GET
http://localhost:8080/api/policy-types/1

❌ If ID not exists (e.g. 999)
http://localhost:8080/api/policy-types/999